:289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:32:18.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"60d15d181a8f78fea8020fcff4e00fa7c295232d","tid":1534514,"uid":237747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:35:36.000Z","msg":"大家有無其他民建聯資訊share"},{"pid":"ba51afd5bdf9d25d0d46e70d6d9bf48eb4d2322d","tid":1534514,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"[法律] [一石二鳥] 教你點攞法庭命令迫黨鐵交太子站CCTV 再告埋香港警察同港鐵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534194</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">有冇人識831太子車廂嘅人 佢哋出嚟先可以拎CCTV 睇下有冇人死</span></strong><br />\n</span><br />\n個撚個話關心義士 去太子送花<br />\n<